I am writing to formally resign from my position as a solution Engineer at Logiciel Services, effective July 1, 2024. I am currently observing the probation period at Logiciel, so please accept my resignation and relieve me of my duties accordingly.

After careful consideration, I have decided to pursue new opportunities and will no longer be able to continue my role at the company effective July 1, 2024.

Please consider this letter as my official notice of resignation. 

Thank you for the support and opportunities provided during my tenure at Logiciel Services. It has been a valuable experience, and I am grateful for the time I have spent with the team.
